## Coastal / Water Activities

Sea, beach, river aur lake wali activities. Yahan common cheez — **paani**, isliye PFD (life jacket), swimming check aur Coast Guard/tourism permits baar-baar aate hain.

### 1. Scuba Diving
**Desc:** Cylinder aur breathing gear ke saath paani ke andar deep jaakar marine life dekhna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Certified dive operator (PADI/SSI) aur safe dive site choose karo, season ke hisaab se (Andaman/Lakshadweep best Oct-May).
2. Coast Guard / marine authority / Wildlife dept se permits lo; protected reef me extra clearance.
3. Medical fitness check (PADI medical form), swimming ability confirm, insurance.
4. Certified instructors, safe ratio (1:2 se 1:4).
5. Equipment check: cylinder, regulator, BCD, mask, fins, dive computer; oxygen + first-aid boat par.
6. Pre-dive briefing: hand signals, buddy system, max depth, no-deco limits, emergency ascent.
7. Boat se site, controlled descent, supervise, phir safe ascent + safety stop.
8. Post-dive debrief, gear rinse, fly-after-diving rule (18-24 ghante no flying).

