### 2. Snorkeling
**Desc:** Mask, snorkel tube aur fins pehen kar paani ki surface se hi coral aur fish dekhna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Shallow, clear-water reef spot choose karo (kam current, achhi visibility).
2. Reef access permit lo aur boat operator license verify karo.
3. Basic swimming comfort check; non-swimmers ke liye life jacket compulsory.
4. Mask, snorkel, fins, float tubes; reef-safe sunscreen aur rash guard.
5. Briefing: snorkel se breathing, mask defog, buddy system, coral touch mat karo.
6. Trained lifeguard/guide ke saath defined area me hi rakho.
7. Continuous head-count; weak swimmers guide ke paas.
8. Wapas aakar gear rinse + marine conservation reminder.

