### 3. Surfing
**Desc:** Surfboard par khade hokar samundar ki lehron (waves) ko ride karna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Consistent waves wala beach + sahi season (West coast SW monsoon ke aas-paas best swells).
2. Registered surf school/club se coordinate; local panchayat/authority permission.
3. Beginners ke liye foam/soft-top boards + leash; level-wise groups.
4. Lifeguard cover, flotation aid, first-aid; rip-current areas mark.
5. Land par 'pop-up', paddling aur balance ki dry practice.
6. Briefing: leash use, board control, distance, rip current se nikalna.
7. Whitewater (chhoti waves) me supervised start, phir aage.
8. Board rinse, debrief, ocean-safety habits reinforce.

