### 4. Kayaking
**Desc:** Double-bladed paddle wale chhote kayak me baith kar river, lake ya sea me chalna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Water body + grade choose karo (calm backwater/lake vs sea vs rapids) level ke hisaab se.
2. River/lake/sea permits; river ke case me local admin/forest clearance.
3. Sit-in/sit-on-top kayaks, paddles, helmets, PFD sabke liye.
4. Swimming check; weather aur tide/current forecast.
5. Basic strokes, wet-exit aur capsize recovery shallow me sikhao.
6. Trained guide ke saath; lead aur sweep kayaker fix.
7. Defined route, regular head-count, throw-bag/rescue kayak ready.
8. Gear collect, dry, quick debrief.

