### 5. Canoeing
**Desc:** Open canoe me single-blade paddle se calm rivers, lakes ya backwaters me chalna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Calm water route plan; distance capacity ke hisaab se.
2. Boating permit lo, operator license verify.
3. Canoes, single-blade paddles, life jackets, bailers.
4. Weather + water-level check; swimming ability note.
5. Paddling technique, steering, weight-balance kinare par.
6. Trained guide; buddy/lead-sweep system.
7. Planned route, head-count, rest points fix.
8. Equipment count, dry storage, safety debrief.

