### 6. White-Water Rafting
**Desc:** Inflatable raft me team ke saath river ke rapids ko paddle karke paar karna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. River stretch + rapid grade (I-V) + season (Ganga rafting approx Sep-Jun).
2. Registered rafting operator hire karo; river-running permit lo.
3. Self-bailing raft, helmets, PFDs, paddles, rescue throw-bags.
4. Medical/swimming status; age aur grade restrictions follow.
5. Certified river guide + safety kayaker.
6. Briefing: paddle commands, 'high-side', swim position (feet downstream), girne par kya karna.
7. Launch, rapids sequence me run, guide ke commands follow.
8. Take-out par head-count, gear collect, incident debrief.

