### 7. Sailing / Yachting
**Desc:** Hawa (wind) ke power se sails wale boat ya yacht ko sea ya lake me chalana.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Sailing waters + boat type (dinghy for beginners, keelboat/yacht for cruising).
2. Marina/harbour berth + sailing permit; coastal ke liye Coast Guard/port clearance.
3. Boat & safety gear inspect: sails, rigging, life jackets, VHF radio, flares, anchor.
4. Weather/wind forecast (Beaufort scale); route/float plan file.
5. Certified skipper/instructor; crew ko points of sail aur basic knots sikhao.
6. Briefing: man-overboard drill, boom se sar bachana, tacking/gybing commands.
7. Controlled conditions me rigging, launching, sailing defined area me.
8. Berth par boat secure, gear dry, debrief.

