### 15. Free Diving (Breath-Hold Diving)
**Desc:** Bina cylinder ke, sirf ek saans rok kar paani ke andar deep dive karna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Clear, calm, deep-enough site + achhi visibility.
2. Certified freediving school (AIDA/SSI/PADI Freediver) se train; site access permit.
3. Medical fitness (ENT/lung), mask, fins, wetsuit, weight belt.
4. Buddy system **COMPULSORY** — ek diver, ek surface safety hamesha.
5. Breath-hold, equalization, relaxation shallow me sikhao.
6. Briefing: never dive alone, shallow-water blackout, slow ascent, recovery breaths.
7. Progressive depth me supervised dives; buddy hamesha watch kare.
8. Debrief, hydration, over-exertion se bacho.

