2. Fishing permit/license (state fisheries/forest); protected species & no-fishing zones avoid.
3. Boat + experienced boatman; rods, reels, bait, tackle check.
4. Weather aur tide check; life jackets aur first-aid.
5. Briefing: rod handling, hook safety, catch-and-release, sustainable limits.
6. Charter boat se planned spot, lines safely cast.
