### 17. Water Zorbing
**Desc:** Hawa-bhare transparent plastic ball ke andar baith kar paani ki surface par roll/float karna.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Shallow, calm, enclosed water area (pool/lake edge) + controlled depth.
2. Setup permission; operator equipment certification verify.
3. Zorb ball inspect: seams, zip, air pressure, blower working.
4. Health check (no claustrophobia/heart issues); time limit set (air limited hai).
5. Briefing: andar balance, ghabrana mat, time limit, exit signal.
6. Ball me air bhar kar participant bithao, zip secure.
7. Trained operator rope/boundary se control; lifeguard standby; fixed time me wapas.
8. Ball deflate, participant nikalo, quick debrief.

