### 4. Sport Climbing
**Desc:** Pre-fixed bolts par rope clip karke chadhna — rock climbing ka safer, competition-friendly form.

**Organise kaise kare:**
1. Bolted crag ya artificial climbing wall identify (indoor walls easy).
2. Qualified instructor + belayer; route grades set.
3. Venue permission/booking — gym ya outdoor crag ke liye local club.
4. Equipment: dynamic rope, harness, quickdraws, belay device, helmet, climbing shoes.
5. Safety brief: clipping technique, lead belaying, fall practice, signals.
6. Routes colour/grade ke hisaab se mark; warm-up ke baad climb.
7. First-aid + equipment regular inspect.
8. Competition format me timing + judging panel (speed/lead/boulder).

