## Quick Recap / Cheat-sheet

**Organising (har activity):** *Aim → Season → Permit → People → Guide → Gear → Logistics → Brief → Do it → Debrief.*

**Association yaad rakhne ka shortcut:**

| Group | Yaad rakho |
|---|---|
| Mountaineering / climbing / trek | **IMF** (apex, New Delhi) + institutes HMI, NIM, ABVIMAS, NIMAS |
| Skiing / snowboarding | **Ski & Snowboard India (SSI)** — FIS+IOA recognised (WGFI sirf historical) |
| Sailing / windsurf / kite | **YAI** |
| Surfing / SUP | **SFI** (Surfing Federation of India) |
| Kayak / canoe | **IKCA** |
| Rafting | **IAPRO** + ATOAI norms |
| Paragliding / hang / balloon / paramotor / skydive | **Aero Club of India (ACI)** + DGCA; paragliding bhi **PAI** |
| Cycling / MTB | **CFI** |
| Motorbike / ATV | **FMSCI** |
| Archery | **AAI** |
| Orienteering | **OFI** |
| Trek/adventure camps (youth) | **YHAI**; cadets → **NCC** |
| Wildlife safari | **NTCA** + State Forest Depts |
| Water sports training institute | **NIWS, Goa** |
| Bungee/zipline/jet-ski/parasail/banana boat | **No single federation** — Ministry of Tourism + ATOAI guidelines + state tourism |

**PPDT story:**
- **Hero:** Naam + Umar + Role + Leadership — pehli line me.
- **OLQs:** 4 factors se 4-5 qualities, *action ke through* (show, don't tell).
- **Flow:** Situation → Problem → Plan/Action → Team Effort → Positive Result.
- **Conclusion:** Result + Appreciation + Learning. Hamesha positive, complete, team ke saath.

All the best aspirant — har picture par **4 minute ka timer** laga kar practice karo. Speed aur structure dono aa jaayenge.
